{% comment %}
  What We Stand For section with accordion functionality
{% endcomment %}

<section class="core-values-homepage-section">
  <div class="core-values-section__inner">
    <div class="core-values-section__image">
      <img
        src="{{ section.settings.image | image_url }}"
        class="core-values-section__image-image"
        width="400"
        height="600"
      >
    </div>
    <div class="core-values-content">
      <h2 class="core-values-title">WHAT WE STAND FOR</h2>

      <div class="core-values-accordion">
        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">▶</span>
            <h3 class="accordion-title">LOVE THE JOURNEY</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              THE PEAK IS A MOMENT. THE CLIMB IS THE LIFE. WE THINK EVERYONE BUILDS A STRONGER VERSION OF THEMSELVES
              WHEN YOU SWEAT TOGETHER.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">▶</span>
            <h3 class="accordion-title">TRACK THE TRUTH</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              START POINT. END POINT. THE SPACE IN BETWEEN IS YOURS TO SHAPE. MEASURE THE WORK, WATCH THE EVOLUTION.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">▶</span>
            <h3 class="accordion-title">PLAY THE LONG GAME</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>
              WE DON’T CHASE QUICK WINS. WE BUILD THINGS THAT OUTLAST THE SEASON. PATIENCE IS THE LOUDEST STATEMENT.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
            <span class="accordion-icon">▶</span>
            <h3 class="accordion-title">NO LOSSES, ONLY LESSONS</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>WHEN SOMETHING DOESN’T WORK OUT, WE FIGURE OUT WHY AND COME BACK MORE EXPERIENCED.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .core-values-homepage-section {
    font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0;
    height: 600px;
  }

  .core-values-section__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .core-values-section__image {
    height: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .core-values-section__image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .core-values-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 3rem;
    background-color: #e6e6e6;
    height: 100%;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .core-values-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
    color: #000;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .core-values-accordion {
    width: 100%;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .accordion-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    overflow: hidden;
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    transform-origin: center;
    background-color: transparent;
    will-change: transform, flex;
  }

  .accordion-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .accordion-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .accordion-icon {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-right: 1rem;
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .accordion-title {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin: 0;
    color: #000;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
  }

  .accordion-content {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1), padding 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1),
      opacity 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    padding: 0;
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .accordion-item:hover {
    z-index: 2;
    flex: 2.2;
    min-height: 150px;
    /* transform: scale(1.02); */
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);
  }

  .accordion-item:hover .accordion-header {
    padding: 2rem 0 1rem 0;
  }

  /* .accordion-item:hover .accordion-title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  } */

  .accordion-item:hover .accordion-icon {
    /* transform: rotate(90deg) scale(1.1); */
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  .accordion-item:hover .accordion-content {
    max-height: 200px;
    padding: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .accordion-content p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin: 0;
    color: #000;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    padding-left: 2.2rem;
    transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0.1s;
    transform: translateY(10px);
  }

  .accordion-item:hover .accordion-content p {
    transform: translateY(0);
    color: #333;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .core-values-section__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
    }

    .core-values-homepage-section {
      height: auto;
    }

    .core-values-content {
      height: auto;
      min-height: 500px;
    }

    .core-values-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }
</style>

